JOBURGWe discover Nomads and Co. is more than just a trendy co-working space and find out more about the upcoming Photo and Film Expo. We also look at coastal property trends and explore whether holiday homes have been affected by the current economic climate. KWAZULU-NATALWe visit Antique Caf for some good eats and find out what it takes to be a South African barista champ. We also look at how the popularity of eco-, wildlife and country estates around KwaZulu-Natal continues to be on the rise.Durban PMB &amp; the Midlands PRETORIAWe visit the award-winning fusion restaurant La Pentola to see what all the fuss is about and look at the impact a new fibre-optic network installed in Tshwane will have on telecommunications. CAPE TOWNWe break bread at the new artisan eatery, Loaves on Long, and then take a trip to explore glorious Betty s Bay. We also look at how property prices in the CBD are still on the rise. Visit yourneighbourhood.co.za, like YourNeighbourhoodZA on Facebook and follow YourHoodZA on Twitter.